      "order_number": 97,
      "text": "So I, I feel like, I feel like she's, like, harder than any of the dogs I've had in my life."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 410.27,
      "start_time": 410.02,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 98,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 411.3,
      "start_time": 410.28,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 99,
      "text": "It'll, it'll get quick though."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 413.03,
      "start_time": 412.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 100,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 417.36,
      "start_time": 413.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 101,
      "text": "They, once they get settled down they're so good with kids too."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 417.81,
      "start_time": 417.51,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 102,
      "text": "That'll"
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 420.42,
      "start_time": 417.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 103,
      "text": "be, that's kind of why we, why, why we went that route this time."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 421.15,
      "start_time": 420.69,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 104,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 423.58,
      "start_time": 421.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 105,
      "text": "I had, like, the golden doodle and the Labradoodle."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 427.34,
      "start_time": 423.59,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 106,
      "text": "They, and they were four and, and five and I thought they're gonna be around forever."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 431,
      "start_time": 427.35,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 107,
      "text": "And then this summer one had cancer got like a freaking tumor on its shoulder."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 433.67,
      "start_time": 431.01,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 108,
      "text": "The size of a softball within like a week, had to put her down."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 439.2,
      "start_time": 433.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 109,
      "text": "And then the other one, the, the, the Labradoodle or the golden doodle, she, uh, had like kidney failure, like a month later."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 439.82,
      "start_time": 439.21,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 110,
      "text": "It was crazy."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 440.82,
      "start_time": 440.25,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 111,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 441.83,
      "start_time": 441.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 112,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 443.68,
      "start_time": 442.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 113,
      "text": "that's terrible."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 445.15,
      "start_time": 444.41,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 114,
      "text": "Yeah, bad luck."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 451.66,
      "start_time": 445.16,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 115,
      "text": "So, I, I don't know, kind of a, it was like, weirdly, kind of nice not having a dog for a little bit."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 457.09,
      "start_time": 451.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 116,
      "text": "But I, I like him around so I figured my, like, one son doesn't sleep at all anyways now."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 461.73,
      "start_time": 457.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "84573cf6-634d-4690-ac5d-acd046d8fef5",
      "order_number": 117,
      "text": "So I was like, let's just kind of get it all out at once rather than him start sleeping and then I have to do with a puppy and three more."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 466.27,
      "start_time": 465.29,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 118,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 467.75,
      "start_time": 466.28,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 119,
      "text": "She's not chilling."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
      "end_time": 469.2,
      "start_time": 468.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "fed04835-34a3-4e37-b71c-3608cb8937f8",
      "order_number": 120,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "3626d8f5-7095-4c65-8c2d-f4fba3648739",
      "recording_id": "05631c48-55fd-410e-9b39-9686b9fea467",
